This paper is primarily focused on the training of large neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves decentralized training, which could also fall under the categories of distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The use of mixture of experts is a common technique in control systems (cs.SY) and neural networks (cs.NE), which could also be relevant to this paper.
